title: Bonding Curve Supply should be limited to 25M 20M
body:
Bonding curve supply should be limited to 25M. At any point of time, the supply from Bonding curve should not exceed 25M.
Limiting the supply should enable sustainable token value , hence better suited to being used as utility token in the eco-system.
choices: Yes, Limit the Bonding curve to 25M supply
No, let the unlimited supply inflate the token market cap
